subSubSection.paragraph:
Paleoenvironment.
The occurrences in offshore clays (Lăpugiu de Sus, Baden, Bad Vöslau, Möllersdorf, Forchtenau) would suggest a preference for middle to outer neritic environments. This contrasts with frequent occurrences in shallow water settings with sea grass meadows (e.g. Gainfarn; 

Zuschin 
et al
. 2007

). Maybe the species had a broad habitat tolerance, or the robust shells have been transported into offshore settings.

